From cou.: 13 Due to the spectral quality, the lH VT-NMR spectra of hydrido region of complexes 2 and 3 will be discussed in detail by means of dynamic models in the next section, while those of complex 1 are now analysed in a qualitative way.
From Soup: 13 Due to the spectral quality, the l H VT-NMR spectra of hydrido region of complexes 2 and 3 will be discussed in detail by means of dynamic models in the next section, while those of complex 1 are now analysed in a qualitative way.
