From cou.: 41 All temperatures (K) were calibrated with 4% methanol in methanol-d4 (range 300–180 K) and 80% ethylene glycol in DMSO-d6 (range 380–300 K) by measuring the frequency difference between the OH and the CH3 (methanol) or CH2 (glycol) signals.
From Soup: 41 All temperatures (K) were calibrated with 4% methanol in methanol- d 4 (range 300–180 K) and 80% ethylene glycol in DMSO- d 6 (range 380–300 K) by measuring the frequency difference between the OH and the CH 3 (methanol) or CH 2 ( glycol ) signals.
